{"type":null,"faqId":33387,"title":"如何关闭输入法振动","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-size:0pt;border::thin solid black;color:black;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>进入华为输入法设置界面，点击“虚拟键盘设置”，将“按下时振动提示”下方的滑块拖动到最左侧，即可取消输入时的振动。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>或者直接点击键盘震动快捷图标，将“按下时振动提示”下方的滑块拖动到最左侧，即可取消输入时的振动。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=105472\" style=\"width:2.16875in;height:3.85625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=105473\" style=\"width:2.16875in;height:3.85625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=105474\" style=\"width:2.1666667in;height:3.8506944in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=105475\" style=\"width:2.16875in;height:3.85625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=105476\" style=\"width:2.4041667in;height:4.271528in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s1\"> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=105477\" style=\"width:2.4041667in;height:4.271528in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8089","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748597000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":9,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"输入法,振动","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}